          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700 mb-4">
            Jones Valley homes typically feature 3 to 5 bedrooms, formal living and dining rooms, spacious family rooms, and the generous lot sizes that characterized thoughtful suburban development. Many homeowners have tastefully updated kitchens and bathrooms while preserving the character that makes these homes so appealing. Original hardwood floors, built-in bookcases, and solid craftsmanship define the neighborhood's aesthetic.
          </p>
          <p class="text-lg text-gray-700">
            Your family's time together matters more than housework. While you're cheering at Grissom games, hosting neighborhood gatherings, or simply enjoying a quiet weekend at home, let The Valley Clean Team handle the cleaning. We understand what Jones Valley families value and deliver the consistent, reliable service you deserve.
          </p>
        </div>
        <div class="bg-gradient-to-br from-[#FFA985]/10 to-[#FFC67D]/10 rounded-2xl p-8 border border-[#FFA985]/20">
          <h3 class="text-2xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-6">Jones Valley Home Features:</h3>
          <ul class="space-y-3">
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>2,000-4,500 sq ft</strong> traditional floor plans</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Original hardwood floors</strong> throughout</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Formal living and dining</strong> rooms</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Updated kitchens</strong> with modern finishes</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>3-5 bedrooms</strong> for growing families</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Mature landscaping</strong> and large lots</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
              <Icon name="check" class="w-5 h-5 text-green-500 mt-1 mr-3 flex-shrink-0" />
              <span class="text-gray-700"><strong>Built-in cabinetry</strong> and millwork</span>
            </li>
            <li class="flex items-start">
