          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Work-Schedule Friendly</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">With Research Park just minutes away, many Jones Valley residents work demanding professional jobs. We clean while you're at the office, using the access method you prefer. Come home from work to a pristine house - no weekend cleaning required. Your time off is truly time off.</p>
        </div>

        <div class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-8 shadow-lg border border-gray-200 service-card">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 rounded-full bg-gradient-to-r from-[#FFA985] to-[#FFC67D] flex items-center justify-center mb-4">
            <Icon name="paw" class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
