          <p class="text-gray-600">Jones Valley is a family neighborhood, and that includes furry family members. We use pet-safe, family-friendly products and work comfortably around dogs, cats, and kids. Our team members are parents and pet owners too - we understand the dynamics of busy family homes.</p>
