            <Icon name="bolt" class="w-8 h-8 text-white" />
          </div>
          <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-[#333333] mb-3">Same-Day When You Need It</h3>
          <p class="text-gray-600">Life happens fast. Unexpected guests, post-party cleanup, or just a day when you need help now rather than next week. We offer same-day service when available - call before noon and we'll do our best to accommodate. Your neighborhood connections deserve a home that's always ready.</p>
        </div>

